      "text": "browser-runtime-skill/\n├─ docker-compose.yml        # broker + chrome-runtime\n├─ broker/                   # 控制平面 API/WS/lease/job\n├─ runtime/chrome/           # Chromium+CDP+noVNC image\n├─ extension/                # 真实 Tab Group companion extension\n├─ extractors/               # 站点脚本 registry\n├─ data/                     # sqlite/gitignored\n├─ artifacts/                # HTML/PNG/trace/gitignored\n├─ docs/                     # compose/API/并发策略\n└─ SKILL.md                  # agent 使用协议",
